      "content": "i mean i get that, but i've read online that if the bacteria are gone, taking more meds just messes with my gut health and creates resistance. my doctor didn't really explain why i need the full 10 days if the symptoms are totally gone. isn't it better to just stop once the infection is cleared so i don't cause more problems for myself?",
